<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>MAW KA NUNNAK</title>
<lyrics>[B1]
   ( Halleluijah, Halleluijah Hossana, Halleluijah, Halleluijah Hossana)2

[C1]
   Zungzal nungmi Pathian, Zungzal hmunmi Pathian
   Zeizong vialte uktu, Cungnungbik cu thangthat tuah u
   Zungzal nungmi Pathian, Zungzal hmunmi Pathian
   Zeizong vialte ngeitu, Liannganbik cu thangthat tuah u
   Maw ka zeizong.

[B2]
   Halleluijah Hossana, Halleluijah, Halleluijah Hossana.

[V1]
 Maw ka zeizong, Bawipa cu thangthat
 Maw ka sining, Bawipa cu thangthat,
 Maw ka thlarau, Bawipa cu thangthat
 Ka nunnak cu, Thl ttha in a khahter.

[V2]
 Maw ka nunnak, Bawipa cu thangthat
 Maw ka thinlung, Bawipa cu thangthat,
 Maw ka thlarau, Bawipa cu thangthat
 Ka nunnak cu, Thil ttha in a khahter.</lyrics>
